{"title":"爷爷的军帽","authors":["刘朝"],"dates":[{"year":1995,"month":6,"day":19}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"爷爷的军帽"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刘朝"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"站在暮年布满阳光的巷头"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"爷爷总爱抚摸"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那顶破旧的军帽"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抚摸他枪声中淬火的往事"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抚摸出些可口的情节"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"将我饥饿的童年喂养"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"爷爷的军帽"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鸟瞰过一个民族苦难的行程"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"被那些正义的人们"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用脚步和信念丈量"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每每接近军帽，我"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"总能触摸到雪山、草地的温存"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"苦菜和小米的醇芳"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"爷爷的军帽"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"被血水洗过又被战火烤干"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"淮海的那场风暴"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就差点把爷爷和它一同掀倒"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"爷爷的肋骨间，至今"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我还能摸出锈黑色的金属"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那黄金般的脆响"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多年过去了。如今"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中国的天空高远而明亮"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而爷爷"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只能被嵌在黑色的镜框里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让我仰视"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让我铭记让我怀念"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可爷爷那顶破旧的军帽"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在我感恩的记忆里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"总被深刻地珍藏"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":12,"page_end":12}